---
---
<section class="relative bg-brand-bg py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-12 px-5 sm:px-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.85fr_1.15fr] lg:gap-16 lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal relative">
      <div class="relative bg-brand-secondary/30 p-0.5 shadow-2xl shadow-black/60" style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%);">
        <div class="h-full w-full overflow-hidden" style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%);">
          <img src="/images/powerhub/home/help.webp" alt="Brian Ho, director of Powerhub Electrical, on site in Revesby" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-5 -right-3 bg-brand-secondary px-5 py-3 font-heading font-black uppercase text-brand-bg" style="clip-path: polygon(6% 0, 100% 0, 94% 100%, 0 100%);">
        Brian
        <span class="block text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide opacity-80">Founder &amp; Licensed Electrician</span>
      </div>
      <span class="absolute -left-4 top-10 h-24 w-1.5 -skew-y-12 bg-brand-accent"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 120ms;">
      <p class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-brand-muted">
        <span class="inline-block h-px w-10 bg-brand-accent"></span>
        From the director
      </p>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[clamp(1.9rem,4.5vw,3rem)] font-black uppercase leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.01em] text-brand-text">
        A message from Brian Ho, <span class="text-brand-secondary">director of Powerhub Electrical</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        I started my apprenticeship in my final year of high school and have been in the trade for close to ten years now. I began Powerhub Electrical in 2023 because I wanted a business built on honesty and doing a job properly the first time, not cutting corners to move on to the next one.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl font-body text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-muted">
        That standard doesn't change whether the job is near Epping or out around Revesby Village and the older streets closer to the Georges River. If it's not good enough for my own home, I won't leave it behind in yours.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl font-heading text-lg font-bold italic text-brand-secondary">
        Brian Ho
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
